On the application front, various sectors such as food and beverage, pharmaceuticals, e-commerce, automotive, and others are embracing packaging automation solutions to optimize their packaging workflows. The e-commerce segment, in particular, is experiencing rapid growth driven by the booming online retail sector and the need for efficient packaging solutions to enhance order fulfillment and delivery processes. By leveraging automation technologies, companies operating in the e-commerce space are able to improve operational efficiencies, reduce errors, and meet the growing demand for quick and accurate packaging services.

